    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="STATA-拟合重复测量数据"><a href="#STATA-拟合重复测量数据" class="headerlink" title="STATA 拟合重复测量数据"></a>STATA 拟合重复测量数据</h3><p>研究者对16位手术患者随访了六次疼痛缓解评分，数据格式如下；</p><h4 id="横向数据转换为纵向数据"><a href="#横向数据转换为纵向数据" class="headerlink" title="横向数据转换为纵向数据"></a>横向数据转换为纵向数据</h4><figure class="highlight r"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">reshape long tol, i(id) j(age)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="疼痛缓解评分在6个时间点上的变化探索性分析"><a href="#疼痛缓解评分在6个时间点上的变化探索性分析" class="headerlink" title="疼痛缓解评分在6个时间点上的变化探索性分析"></a>疼痛缓解评分在6个时间点上的变化探索性分析</h4><figure class="highlight r"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">graph twoway (lowess tolerance age)(scatter tolerance age), by(id)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>为了分析个体水平上六次疼痛缓解评分的关联性，以随访患者为随机效应，构建混合效应模型：</p><p>$$y_{ij}=\beta_0+Z_j+\varepsilon_{ij}$$<br>$$Z_j\sim N(0,\sigma^2_u)$$<br>$$\varepsilon_{ij}\sim N(0,\sigma^2_e)$$</p><p>$$\frac{\partial u}{\partial t}<br>= h^2 \left( \frac{\partial^2 u}{\partial x^2} +<br>\frac{\partial^2 u}{\partial y^2} +<br>\frac{\partial^2 u}{\partial z^2}\right)$$</p><figure class="highlight r"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">mixed tol, || id:, covariance(unstructured)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="按照计算方法手动计算ICC"><a href="#按照计算方法手动计算ICC" class="headerlink" title="按照计算方法手动计算ICC"></a>按照计算方法手动计算ICC</h4><figure class="highlight r"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">. disp (<span class="number">.0746477</span>)/(<span class="number">.0746477</span>+<span class="number">.1679431</span>)</div><div class="line"><span class="number">.30771035</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="STATA-自动计算ICC"><a href="#STATA-自动计算ICC" class="headerlink" title="STATA 自动计算ICC"></a>STATA 自动计算ICC</h4><figure class="highlight r"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">. estat icc</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">Intraclass correlation</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">------------------------------------------------------------------------------</div><div class="line">                       Level |        ICC   Std. Err.     [<span class="number">95</span>% Conf. Interval]</div><div class="line">-----------------------------+------------------------------------------------</div><div class="line">                          id |   <span class="number">.3077104</span>   <span class="number">.1220946</span>      <span class="number">.1262871</span>    <span class="number">.5774963</span></div><div class="line">------------------------------------------------------------------------------</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
